OSTREE GPG-SIGN(1)              ostree gpg-sign             OSTREE GPG-SIGN(1)

NAME
       ostree-gpg-sign - Sign a commit

SYNOPSIS
       ostree gpg-sign [OPTIONS...] {COMMIT} {KEY-ID...}

DESCRIPTION
       Add a new signature to a commit for each specified GPG key. Note that
       currently, this will append a new signature even if the commit is
       already signed with a given key.

OPTIONS
       --delete
           Delete signatures having any of the GPG KEY-IDs.

       --gpg-homedir="HOMEDIR"
           GPG Homedir to use when looking for keyrings.

OSTree                                                      OSTREE GPG-SIGN(1)
